Orders

Shipment

Status tracking


Each service:

Runs independently

Has its own database

Deploys independently


This ensures:

Scalability

Clear ownership

Independent releases



---

🗄 6️⃣ Data Layer

Under each service:

Primary database (Postgres, MySQL, MongoDB)

Redis cache

Read replicas

Search engine (Elasticsearch)

Message queue (Kafka)


Important: Resolvers should NEVER directly join across services. They communicate via GraphQL federation, not shared databases.


