⚡ 7️⃣ Performance Optimization Layer

Where senior-level knowledge shines.

1. DataLoader

Fixes N+1 problem by batching DB queries.

2. Caching

Redis at resolver level

CDN at edge

In-memory caching for hot data


3. Pagination

Always use cursor-based pagination for large datasets.

4. Query Complexity Control

Prevent expensive nested queries.


